result.item_name: Essential Proactive Support
result.item_description:
Digital Signage Service Fee per month - 36+ Months (Level2)

The Essential Proactive Support package provides Pro-active Monitoring on devices - most of the know issues are identified before the issues occurs, and before the customer knows. A case is automatically created based on issue tracking scripts installed on devices. The issue tracker feature are based on known issues. Once the case is created, it will be assigned to a support technician for resolve remotely or over the phone. Any on-site technical support is an optional extra.


  • Essential Proactive Support provides:
  • Telephone and Email support for Level 1 Support team
  • Access to trained Digital Media specialists
  • Proactive remote monitoring to all devices
  • Automatic case creation & notification based on issue tracking scripts
  • Hours of operation; 8.00am to 6.00pm (AEST) Business Days(excluding public holidays)
